<div class="grid_12">
  <p>
    Choose a collection to work with.  If you have &quot;write&quot; access to
    a collection, you can add new objects or update existing objects.  Contact
    UC3 if you don't see the collection you need.  Whatever else we need to say.
  </p>

  <p>
    We really don't know what is happening with the profile service right
    now, so we're not sure how permissions or number of objects will ever
    get populated.
  </p>

  <h3>Collections</h3>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 40%;">Collection</th>
        <th style="width: 20%;">Permissions</th>
        <th style="width: 20%;"># Objects</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @grps.each do |grp| %>
      <tr class="<%=cycle('even', 'odd') %>">
        <td><%= grp.description %></td>
        <td><%= permissions(grp.permission(current_user.login)) %></td>
        <td style="text-align:right;">random! <%= formatted_int(grp.object_count) %></td>
      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
<div class="grid_4 sidebar">
  <h3>Search my collections</h3>
  <% form_tag({:controller => 'search', :action => 'by_id'}, :method => :get) do %>
    <%= text_field_tag 'id', 'enter primary id here' %>
    <%= submit_tag('Go') %>
  <% end %>
 
  <p>You can look up a known primary ID across all collections. Once you select
    a collection, you will be able to search by title, creator or local ID.
  </p>
  <h3 style="color:#cc0000;">Alert</h3>
</div>
